  "page": "City Watch of Lannisport",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">City Watch of Lannisport</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e9/Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg/300px-Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e9/Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg/450px-Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e9/Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg/600px-Lannisportguardbyrvalle.jpg 2x\" /></a><div style=\"font-size: 100%; margin-bottom:10px;\">A Lannisport guard</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Type</th><td>\nCity watch</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>City Watch of Lannisport</b> is the formal policing and protection unit of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. Supported by the wealthy <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, they are known to be well-trained compared to those of <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_Oldtown\" title=\"City Watch of Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=City_Watch_of_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After losing to <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls_tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whitewalls tourney\">Whitewalls tourney</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> briefly considered joining the City Watch of Lannisport or Oldtown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=City_Watch_of_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1174/\">Military Questions</a> (June 21, 2001)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_